{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3075949c-ed74-4e13-999d-e3cc9b6e513f","agentId":"a3fedc0e690a7fa51","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Fix two issues in the `api_performance_saldo` route in `/root/jake_desktop/app.py`.\n\n## Issues to fix\n\n**Issue 1:** The route returns HTTP 500 for an unknown agency. It should return 404. Also the error message echoes the user-supplied agency name — replace with a generic message.\n\n**Issue 2:** The test `test_saldo_agencia_invalida` asserts `status_code == 500`, which needs to be updated to `404`.\n\n**Issue 3 (minor):** Move the cache check before the token lookup, consistent with the existing pattern in `api_relatorios_insights`.\n\n## How to find the code\n\nSearch for `api_performance_saldo` in `/root/jake_desktop/app.py`. The function is around line 801.\n\n## Fix 1: Route code\n\nFind this block in `api_performance_saldo`:\n```python\n    token_fn = _META_TOKENS.get(agency)\n    if not token_fn:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": f\"Agência '{agency}' não configurada\"}), 500\n    token = token_fn()\n    if not token:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": f\"Token da agência '{agency}' não configurado\"}), 500\n\n    cache_key = f\"saldo:{agency}:{account_id}\"\n    now = time.time()\n    if cache_key in _perf_saldo_cache:\n        cached = _perf_saldo_cache[cache_key]\n        if now - cached[\"ts\"] < _PERF_SALDO_TTL:\n            return jsonify(cached[\"data\"])\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```python\n    token_fn = _META_TOKENS.get(agency)\n    if not token_fn:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": \"Agência não encontrada\"}), 404\n\n    cache_key = f\"saldo:{agency}:{account_id}\"\n    now = time.time()\n    if cache_key in _perf_saldo_cache:\n        cached = _perf_saldo_cache[cache_key]\n        if now - cached[\"ts\"] < _PERF_SALDO_TTL:\n            return jsonify(cached[\"data\"])\n\n    token = token_fn()\n    if not token:\n        return jsonify({\"error\": \"Token da agência não configurado\"}), 500\n```\n\n## Fix 2: Test file\n\nIn `/root/jake_desktop/tests/test_performance_api.py`, find:\n```python\ndef test_saldo_agencia_invalida(client):\n    r = client.get(\"/api/performance/saldo/agencia_inexistente/act_123456789\")\n    assert r.status_code == 500\n```\n\nReplace with:\n```python\ndef test_saldo_agencia_invalida(client):\n    r = client.get(\"/api/performance/saldo/agencia_inexistente/act_123456789\")\n    assert r.status_code == 404\n```\n\n## After fixing\n\nRun tests to confirm they pass:\n```bash\ncd /root/jake_desktop && .venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/test_performance_api.py -k \"saldo\" -v\n```\nExpected: 5 PASSED\n\nThen commit:\n```bash\ncd /root && git add jake_desktop/app.py jake_desktop/tests/test_performance_api.py\ngit commit -m \"fix: api_performance_saldo retorna 404 para agência inválida\"\n```\n\nReport: DONE or BLOCKED"},"uuid":"1ebecea6-6b3d-466b-aadb-4d382b87e9f5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:19:50.755Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/root","sessionId":"1416e8fb-06a0-4c7e-ad11-edf123559c87","version":"2.1.80","gitBranch":"main","slug":"sprightly-kindling-hamster"}
